videos.description: After Trae Young scores a layup, he finds Brady Manek on the next possession down court for a layup.
videos.headline: Young contributes on back-to-back baskets

videos.description: Devonte' Graham finds a cutting Mitch Lightfoot who scores for Kansas.
videos.headline: Graham's nice feed sets up Lightfoot layup

videos.description: Kameron McGusty gets two defenders in the air, allowing him to score plus a foul for Oklahoma.
videos.headline: McGusty fakes and scores and-1 layup

videos.description: Trae Young gets pass a defender and throws up a lob to Khadeem Lattin who dunks it home.
videos.headline: Young connects with Lattin for alley-oop

videos.description: Trae Young shows off his great court vision to find Brady Manek for a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Young's great no-look pass sets up Manek 3-pointer

videos.description: After some good ball movement by Oklahoma, Trae Young heads up pass leads to Jamuni McNeace jamming it home.
videos.headline: Young's extra pass leads to McNeace dunk

videos.description: Jamuni McNeace rejects a layup attempt allowing Trae Young to score a tough layup on the other end.
videos.headline: McNeace block leads to Young layup

videos.description: Oklahoma head coach Lon Kruger urges his team to keep working and hoping his team can limit Kansas' 3-point efficiency.
videos.headline: Kruger happy with Oklahoma's ball movement in 1st half

videos.description: Udoka Azubuike powers down a dunk over a defender for Kansas.
videos.headline: Azubuike hammers down a one-handed jam

videos.description: Trae Young hits a deep 3-pointer and follows it up with a nice layup to get Oklahoma within two.
videos.headline: Young hits from Curry range, follows with layup

videos.description: Trae Young stays inbounds, gets pass Udoka Azubuike and hits 3 from way downtown.
videos.headline: Young avoids a defender and drains deep 3

videos.description: Devonte' Graham misses a layup but Lagerald Vick jams it home.
videos.headline: Vick dunks home the missed shot

videos.description: Trae Young drives and finds Christian James who drains a 3 to give Oklahoma the lead.
videos.headline: Young nice pass sets up James' big 3-pointer

videos.description: Trae Young is pleased with his efficient play and the way everyone on Oklahoma played in a big home win against the No. 5 Jayhawks.
videos.headline: Young  proud of teammates in win over Kansas

videos.description: Trae Young does it all, scoring 26 points on 7-of-9 shooting and dishing out nine assists to propel No. 12 Oklahoma to a win over No. 5 Kansas.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Young puts Sooners on his back) 2018/1/23 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Young puts Sooners on his back

videos.description: Fueled by Trae Young's 26 points and nine assists, the No. 12 Sooners close the game on an 11-2 run to top the No. 5 Jayhawks 85-80.
videos.headline: Oklahoma finishes strong to beat Kansas

videos.description: Tom Crean joins SVP to talk about what he called Trae Young's best game of the year against Kansas.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Analysis (Crean: Young's vision 'key to the game') 2018/01/23 ESHEET SVP SC

videos.headline: Crean: Young's vision 'key to the game'
